I came because I needed to tell you something.

16
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,600
Kim Ram Woo.

17
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:24,520
You'll die in a week.

18
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,520
What?

19
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:30,600
You'll die in 176 hours, 12 minutes, and 35 seconds.

20
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:33,300
I'll die in a week?

21
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,600
Yes.

22
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:36,240
How do you know that?

23
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:37,820
Are you the Grim Reaper?

